description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if all of the following occur during the Oklahoma City Thunder vs. Los Angeles Lakers game originally scheduled for February 9, 2026, 10:00 PM ET:

-Austin Reaves scores 30 or more points

-Jalen Williams scores 20 or more points

-Chet Holmgren records 2 or more blocks

-LeBron James records 6 or more assists

Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed.

If this game is canceled or postponed past February 23, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to “No”.

If a listed player does not participate for any reason in the Oklahoma City Thunder vs. Los Angeles Lakers game originally scheduled for February 9, 2026, 10:00 PM ET, this market will resolve to “No”.

The resolution source will be the official NBA box score as published on NBA.com.
